Hello dear devs,

Attaching as requested. The monitor is LG 34WN80C-B.
Might help, I have been using following commands to switch between inputs:

ddcutil setvcp xf4 x00d1 --i2c-source-addr=x50 --noverify #Switch to USB-C
ddcutil setvcp xf4 x0090 --i2c-source-addr=x50 --noverify #Switch to HDMI-1

Thank you for developing and maintaining ddccontrol.

Cheers!
Aslan

